@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jagbil(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v1 = (wp.exp(v0) - wp.cos(0.06))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.50) - (v0 + 0.80 / v0 + 0.21)) + wp.cos((v2 + 0.02 - tmp + 0.49)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.82)) * wp.cos(0.33))
    tmp = 0.84
    tmp = (0.17 + wp.cos((v0 + 0.30 - v1 + 0.75)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.18)) / (0.18 - (v0 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.85)))
    v2 = wp.exp((v1 / 0.70))
    data[tid] = v0
